00:24:52,597 --> 00:24:58,740
events like that, like symphony tours are another good example. I think they're great in elevating

289
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:03,202
the awareness of gay music within a larger community, getting people.

290
00:25:03,522 --> 00:25:08,485
who might not be familiar with game music, more acquainted with it, and to understand that it

291
00:25:08,525 --> 00:25:14,669
really isn't the bleeps and bloops of yesteryear, that it is something that has grown as games have

